text: José de Jesús González Muñoz (born 19 November 1998) is a Mexican professional footballer who plays as a forward for Leones Negros UdeG on loan from Guadalajara. == Personal life == His partner is singer and dancer Sabina Hidalgo, who is member of the group Now United. ==References== ==External links== * * Jose González at Flashscore * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican footballers Category:Mexican expatriate footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:C.D.
